{"id": 2422, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都看腻了英雄电影里的哪些反派设定套路？", "description": "总是把坏蛋的形象整成伤疤脸没鼻子，对真正遭受这些创伤的人来说公平吗？啊！（题图来自：istock © DanielVilleneuve ）", "record_count": 17384, "comment_count": 44, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180614184422ZUnQkHDba9wLx3Ru.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-20T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4392, "title": "你都看腻了英雄电影里的哪些反派设定套路？", "content": "你都看腻了英雄电影里的哪些反派设定套路?", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 287242, "content": "外表不是满脸褶子就是缺鼻少眼，仿佛常患皮肤病", "image": "img/option/option/20180614211332OAl3tsjaGzQKR1br.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287243, "content": "同卵双胞胎里至少有一个是坏人", "image": "img/option/option/20180614211513Ku9cVPbCRvwemgLJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287249, "content": "干掉主角不用子弹，而总要选最终会被破解的复杂机械", "image": "img/option/option/20180614233101kRrzpCEl4wVitD6g.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287250, "content": "或早或晚都会对主角女友/亲友下至少一次手", "image": "img/option/option/201806142349485sIliN4j23CuX8Fk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287252, "content": "大反派总是体贴地先派虾兵蟹将让主角打怪升级", "image": "img/option/option/201806142350563VHeUJp7oOaE0TrY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287254, "content": "和主角一起成长的兄弟/闺蜜，为反转会变成终极boss", "image": "img/option/option/20180615010419xh2XKnDi5wtF4bRy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287301, "content": "和主角比，总是一嘴的口音，一听就不是本地人", "image": "img/option/option/20180615120752rt3FHI6RWnd2yaAc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 287314, "content": "动机莫名奇妙，全程死磕都是因为和主角“命运的羁绊”", "image": "img/option/option/20180615123441hZ4dHExFRLuAcwsn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}